TT 6036 "We'll take a look anyway." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_ON_TRACK__040__M__1
TT 6037 "All right... So, any tower here or...?" VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__010__M__1
TT 6038 "You're right!" VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__023__M__1
TT 6039 "We're back on track then, let's go!" VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__030__M__1
