TT 6041 "Later, yes..." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__040__M__1
TT 6042 "Yes, soon. We'll find our chapel and we'll see." VO__AMICIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__080__M__1
