TT 6595 "They imprisoned him..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__030__M__1
TT 6596 "They were scared of him. Of his power." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__050__M__1
TT 6597 "This is why they built all... this. They were always afraid." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__060__M__1
TT 6598 "He unleashed the rats. They tore through their walls. They couldn't stop them." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__080__M__1
TT 6599 "It started here..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__090__M__1
TT 6600 "The Justinian Plague." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__110__M__1
TT 6601 "So that's why the Macula brought us here?... There has to be something... A scroll... A phial... Something!" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__130__M__1
TT 6602 "Aelia... She failed..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__170__M__1
TT 6603 "She failed, Sophia!" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__190__M__1
TT 6604 "You won't die." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__240__M__1
TT 6605 "No... Hugo... He wasn't meant to die! When they took him from his protector, he lost hope, so he gave in to the Macula and condemned them all!" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__260__M__1
TT 6606 "No... But if one word from her had reached him, he would have known he wasn't alone! He would have lived! And spared millions!" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__270__M__1
TT 6607 "Do you understand? You WON'T die! I'm here for you. And I will give you the life you deserve... A life without fight... Do you want that?" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__280__M__1
TT 6608 "Let's just find ourselves a home." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__300__M__1
TT 6609 "What's going on?" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__560_REMAINS_OF_A_CARRIER__320__M__1
TT 6610 "I think we're fine... Anyone hurt? Hugo?" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__012__M__1
TT 6611 "Yes... I'm sorry you had to see that... The Macula lured you in..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__030__M__1
TT 6612 "Yes... but you'll live. That's what's most important." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__060__M__1
TT 6613 "You're right..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__080__M__1
TT 6614 "Listen... there will always be people who do terrible things... that's how the world is... But you have to trust in your own goodness. And goodness of others. People who care. Who want you do be happy. Friends..." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__085__M__1
TT 6615 "Friends make you want to be good, right?" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__110__M__1
TT 6616 "If you doubt it, I understand... but you can trust me." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__140__M__1
TT 6617 "You can trust us." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__145__M__1
TT 6618 "We'll find a place of our own." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__160__M__1
TT 6619 "Let's leave this island." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__165__M__1
TT 6620 "They won't stop us. Everything is different." VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME__190__M__1
TT 6621 "onom" VO__AMICIA__CH11__RTC__570_LETS_GO_HOME_ONOM__030__M__1
TT 6622 "Now Hugo!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER___LAST_STRIKE__010__M__1
TT 6623 "The truth... We found what we came for. And I'm the one to blame." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__ABOUT_MOTHER__020__M__1
TT 6624 "My hero." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__ABOUT_MOTHER__040__M__1
TT 6625 "You mean... the rats?" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__AFTER__005__M__1
TT 6626 "Yes..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__AFTER__020__M__1
TT 6627 "Hugo... Run..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__AFTER_HIT__020__M__1
TT 6628 "Are you not planning to evacuate?" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__ANY_EVACUATION__010__M__1
