TT 6631 "No!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__BREAK_JARS_1__010__M__1
TT 6632 "Oh please, no..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__BREAK_JARS_2__010__M__1
TT 6633 "Great..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__BREAK_JARS_3__010__M__1
TT 6634 "This is all in vain." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__BRIEFING_REACT__010__M__1
TT 6635 "They won't listen. Let's find Mother." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__BRIEFING_REACT__030__M__1
TT 6636 "There! I could trap him... in that room..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CELL_HELPER__010__M__1
