TT 6639 "No way out..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CELLS__010__M__1
TT 6640 "Come, we'll cross." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__COME_CLOSER__010__M__1
TT 6641 "What?..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION__010__M__1
TT 6642 "You fed her a lie!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION__030__M__1
TT 6643 "Go to Hell, you bastard!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_KITCHEN__013__M__1
TT 6644 "No... No! You won't get him..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_KITCHEN__023__M__1
TT 6645 "Come on!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_LOCKED__010__M__1
TT 6646 "Get back to them... Go..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__020__M__1
TT 6647 "Go to Hell..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__040__M__1
TT 6648 "You won't have him!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_RUN__060__M__1
TT 6649 "Move..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_STAIRS__020__M__1
TT 6650 "To the right... Come on..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_STAIRS_LOW__010__M__1
TT 6651 "Quick..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONFESSION_STAIRS_LOW__020__M__1
TT 6652 "Yes! That's it!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONTROL_LOST__020__M__1
TT 6653 "You did it..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CONTROL_LOST__030__M__1
TT 6654 "No... Shut up!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_ENTERS__060__M__1
TT 6655 "Ha... Too... noisy..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__010__M__1
TT 6656 "No..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__030__M__1
TT 6657 "No time... quick! Move!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__050__M__1
TT 6658 "It's taking too long... If I could just... lock him up somewhere..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK_HELPER__010__M__1
TT 6659 "Yes... Go... Go!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK_OPEN__010__M__1
TT 6660 "This damn... noise..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK_TRY1__010__M__1
TT 6661 "Faster... Come on, come on!" VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK_TRY2__010__M__1
TT 6662 "Must be a way to get back upstairs..." VO__AMICIA__CH12__CHATTER__DISCOVER_CELLAR__010__M__1
