TT 11035 "That's true." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__200__M__1
TT 11036 "Maybe the Plague would stop... with time..." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__213__M__1
TT 11037 "Fear really clouded our minds, didn't it? Except yours, Protector." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__220__M__1
TT 11038 "Remember that house we have in the mountains. We'll be great there!" VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__226__M__1
TT 11039 "Yes." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__285__M__1
TT 11040 "We'll wait for you. For now we're safer here than outside anyway." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__610_A_BANQUET__295__M__1
