TT 11042 "Amicia..." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__630_THE_BALLROOM__019__M__1
TT 11043 "No! Amicia! No! ... Please." VO__BEATRICE__CH12__RTC__640_DUEL__210__M__1
