TT 11179 "You're going nowhere!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_AGGRESSIVE__010__M__1
TT 11180 "Emilie! I'm here!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__010__M__1
TT 11181 "Let him go, Emilie! He's not the Child of Embers! Come to me!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__030__M__1
TT 11182 "You can! Try! Give me your hand!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_COME_BACK__050__M__1
TT 11183 "EMPTY" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_ENTERS__005__M__1
TT 11184 "Where is she?!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__COUNT_ENTERS__040__M__1
TT 11185 "You chose the hard way!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__040__M__1
TT 11186 "I hear you! Fear makes you sloppy!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__CRANK__060__M__1
TT 11187 "All right, let's play! I'm good at this game, you'll see!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__DOOR_CLOSE__010__M__1
TT 11188 "You're stuck here! Wherever you go, I'll find you! I've been trained for this!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE4__010__M__1
TT 11189 "It hurts terribly, doesn't it?! I can ease the pain! Trust me..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE5__010__M__1
TT 11190 "Your survival instinct... I admire it...  You've been through a lot, I can tell. It makes this even more exciting." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE6__010__M__1
TT 11191 "It's been a while since I hunted... Since I met Emilie... And you are wonderful prey!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE8__010__M__1
TT 11192 "She liked you, you know, Emilie... But you're too much of a threat... For us... For the child!..." VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IDLE_CHASE9__010__M__1
TT 11193 "No! Emilie, quick!" VO__COUNT__CH12__CHATTER__IMPENDING_LAST_STRIKE__020__M__1
