TT 13667 "I want quiet. Kill any trespassers." VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__090__M__1
TT 13668 "Light up the trench! We must buy some time!" VO__LEADER__CH10__CHATTER__POST_WAVE__020__M__1
