TT 13673 "Wrong! We're not working for her anymore..." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__043__M__1
TT 13674 "It's all in the fresco! The rats announce the coming of the Child, and you've seen how hungry they are! So it's simple: we please them, we please the Child, we buy ourselves a seat next to his throne!" VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__046__M__1
TT 13675 "Then the Count will bow before us, and the world will follow." VO__LEADER__CH10__RTC__485_UNEXPECTED_STRIKE__050__M__1
