TT 16673 "Someone's playing games with us! Look for them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 16674 "Help me find who's playing us for fools!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 16675 "Jokers are playing with us! Catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 16676 "You think this is funny, do you?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 16677 "Stop messing about!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 16678 "I know you're around here somewhere! I'll find you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 16679 "With me! Intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__1
TT 16680 "Alert! Help me catch those intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__2
TT 16681 "We've got company! Catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__3
TT 16682 "Stop right now!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 16683 "Stop there immediately!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 16684 "Who are you?! Come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 16685 "I'm stuck now but I'll get you soon!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 16686 "You! You'll see when I find how to reach you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 16687 "I'll find a way to get my hands on you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 16688 "It's not over, I'll get to you somehow..." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 16689 "Fine! I'm blocked now, but not forever!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 16690 "Watch your back, I'll find a way to get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 16691 "No! Someone's down!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 16692 "Man down! Watch out!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 16693 "He got killed! Look out!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 16694 "The fire will root you out of the grass, believe me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 16695 "Try to hide in that grass now!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 16696 "It's not a good idea to hide in the grass!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 16697 "We've got intruders... Come with me!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 16698 "Intruders here! Get them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 16699 "Wake up! We've got intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
TT 16700 "Spread out soldiers! We'll get them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__1
TT 16701 "Split up and find them!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 16702 "Let's spread out and cover the area!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
