TT 16704 "You've run out of choices." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 16705 "Shouldn't have come here!" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
