TT 16707 "The hell started this fire?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__2
TT 16708 "How'd this fire get started?" VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__3
TT 16709 "Try to die with some dignity." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 16710 "Cheer up, we all die someday." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 16711 "Better start praying for your soul." VO__SOLDIER_B1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
