TT 17032 "Looks like we've got some jokers here. Find 'em now!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 17033 "Search the area, there's some jokers nearby!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 17034 "They're taking us for fools?! Do what it takes, catch them!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
TT 17035 "You think this is funny? I'll do whatever it takes to stop ya!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 17036 "Just you wait, I'll find you now." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 17037 "You are not funny! I'll stop your little games." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 17038 "Over here! Intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__1
TT 17039 "Intruders! Come over here!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__2
TT 17040 "Over here! Trespassers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT__001__M__3
TT 17041 "You! Stop!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__1
TT 17042 "Stop where you are!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__2
TT 17043 "You! Too late to run away! Stay there!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_ALONE__001__M__3
TT 17044 "When I find a way, I'll beat you hard!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__1
TT 17045 "I'll get my hands on you, I'll find another path!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__2
TT 17046 "I will get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__3
TT 17047 "I won't be stuck here forever! I'll get you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__4
TT 17048 "Well played so far, but I'll get to you!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 17049 "I won't give up on you! Won't be stuck here for long!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
TT 17050 "Damn! Man down!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__1
TT 17051 "Oh no! He's dead!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__2
TT 17052 "Shit! One of us is dead!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_DYING__001__M__3
TT 17053 "You're gonna burn!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__1
TT 17054 "I'll smoke you out, you little bastard!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__2
TT 17055 "These flames'll get you out of the grass!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_IGNITE__001__M__3
TT 17056 "Catch those intruders! Quick!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__1
TT 17057 "Wake up! We've got trespassers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 17058 "Move fast! Stop the bastards!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
TT 17059 "Don't let them get away! Deploy in the area!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__1
TT 17060 "Fan out and find them!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__2
TT 17061 "Fan out! Intruders breakin' through!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_SPREAD__001__M__3
TT 17062 "Say your prayers!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__1
TT 17063 "You die today!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 17064 "Shouldn't have crossed me!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
TT 17065 "Flames?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__1
TT 17066 "Fire? Can't be!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__2
TT 17067 "Come on! Now a fire?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__BURNING__001__M__3
TT 17068 "Struggling won't help you now!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 17069 "Try not to move so much! I want a clean kill!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 17070 "Looks like this is your last day." VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
TT 17071 "What happened to you? Hey! Can you hear me?!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__1
TT 17072 "Oi! Get up, stop messing around!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__2
TT 17073 "What's wrong with you? Hey!" VO__SOLDIER_B2__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__3
