TT 18641 "You're the Countess' guest aren't you? Are you hurt?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__050__M__1
TT 18642 "We have orders to escort you safely to the palace." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__070__M__1
TT 18643 "You have... guests." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__090__M__1
TT 18644 "Your mother, and a boy." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__605_ESCORT__110__M__1
TT 18645 "Sire! We can't stay here. We'll get her from inside!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__660_NOW_THEY_DIE__075__M__1
TT 18646 "Sire!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__020__M__1
TT 18647 "Sire! We need to evacuate, Sire! It's too late!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__040__M__1
TT 18648 "Sire, your people need you! Sire!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH12__RTC__665_DEVOURED__050__M__1
TT 18649 "He'll die, all right?! Now shut the hell up!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__BEFORE_EXECUTION__035__M__1
TT 18650 "Why do we still want the Child? He'll be the end of us! He ruined everything!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__030__M__1
TT 18651 "Ha... let's hope it works..." VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS__050__M__1
TT 18652 "Does someone know when we're suppose to evacuate?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__010__M__1
TT 18653 "So what if the ground collapses entirely before that?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH13__CHATTER__SOLDIERS_IDLE_2__030__M__1
TT 18654 "You heard the Count! Shoot!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH14__CHATTER__ARCHERS_SHOOTING__010__M__1
TT 18655 "May my faith guide my arm! May it lead to brighter days!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_FOG_IDLE_1__010__M__1
TT 18656 "I'm with you, my lord! Reinforcements are coming!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_1__010__M__1
TT 18657 "I will! Right away!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_3__010__M__1
TT 18658 "Your corrupted blood will soak this ground!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_5__010__M__1
TT 18659 "The Child will save us all!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__CH15__CHATTER__FIGHT_NOFOG_IDLE_1__010__M__1
