TT 18771 "Someone's playing with us! Start looking!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__1
TT 18772 "Someone wants to mess with us! Find out who!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__2
TT 18773 "Someone's trying to fool us! Search for them!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__AGAIN_SEARCH__001__M__3
