TT 18787 "Won't give up that easily, I'll get you somehow." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__5
TT 18788 "I may be blocked now but watch your back!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_BLOCKED__001__M__6
