TT 18796 "With me! Stop the intruders!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__2
TT 18797 "They shouldn't be here! Get them!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_PROPAGATE__001__M__3
