TT 18802 "You think you stand a chance?!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__2
TT 18803 "Better start begging for your life!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__ALERT_TAUNT__001__M__3
