TT 18807 "It was bound to happen." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__1
TT 18808 "Don't be afraid, I never miss." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__2
TT 18809 "Time for you to meet the Lord." VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CAPTURE__001__M__3
