TT 18811 "On your feet! Come on!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__2
TT 18812 "You still with us? Hey!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE__001__M__3
TT 18813 "What happened to him?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__1
TT 18814 "What's he doing lying on the ground?" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__2
TT 18815 "Hey! It's not time for a nap!" VO__SOLDIER_S1__GENERIC__PATROL__CORPSE_AFAR__001__M__3
