TT 19833 "Biết hai đứa ở đâu hả? Nghề của tôi mà, cô em... Dậy thật sớm, quan sát, nghe ngóng rồi nhặt nhạnh từng thông tin!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__028__M__1
TT 19834 "Bởi vậy nên tôi mới biết Arnaud hiện đang ngồi tù." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__030__M__1
TT 19835 "Chú bé choăn choắt này có gì để lão ta lợi dụng nhỉ?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__036__M__1
TT 19836 "Hay phải chăng nhóc có tài năng thiên bẩm chưa thể hiện ra bên ngoài?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__038__M__1
TT 19837 "Thế là hai đứa ăn mừng chiến công bằng cách chè chén với vợ chồng Bá tước xứ Provence?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__045__M__1
TT 19838 "Rồi rồi, động trúng lòng tự ái hả!" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__060__M__1
TT 19839 "Tôi đùa thôi mà. Chỉ là hỏi cho biết cô em coi ai là “bạn” thôi... tôi thích câu trả lời đó đấy. Nào, ta đi dạo thôi." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__401_ANEWDAY__065__M__1
TT 19840 "Hòn đảo... Là bản đồ của cả hòn đảo." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__030__M__1
TT 19841 "Chắc phải mấy trăm năm tuổi rồi... Từ thời Byzantine chăng? Quanh đây có nhiều kiến trúc ở thời đó." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__050__M__1
TT 19842 "Hội nào?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__110__M__1
TT 19843 "Nhưng em không quy phục trước bất kỳ ai. Tôi hiểu." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__150__M__1
TT 19844 "Vậy hai đứa đến đây để tìm thứ gì?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__160__M__1
TT 19845 "Đơn giản thôi... Nếu biểu tượng này ám chỉ những khu vực quan trọng..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__180__M__1
TT 19846 "Còn cái này... Cái này thì quá dễ tìm rồi." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__190__M__1
TT 19847 "Chúng được gọi là Las Madres. “Những Người Mẹ”." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__194__M__1
TT 19848 "Phải... Nghe hơi chán." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__200__M__1
TT 19849 "Nếu nhóc muốn. Tôi nói rồi. Tôi nợ hai đứa mà." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__405_MAP__230__M__1
TT 19850 "Phủi phui cái mồm, đã lên đến nơi đâu..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__030__M__1
TT 19851 "Tôi không thích núi non đâu. Những thứ tôi cần đều nằm hết trên mực nước biển rồi." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__050__M__1
TT 19852 "Thế thì cùng cao và cùng lớn thôi nào." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH__080__M__1
TT 19853 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH_ONOM__010__M__1
TT 19854 "onom" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__420_MOUNTAIN_PATH_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 19855 "Công nhận..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__070__M__1
TT 19856 "Người Con của Than Hồng ạ?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__090__M__1
TT 19857 "Lại còn “The Prima Macula”... Càng ngày càng thú vị đây..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__110__M__1
TT 19858 "Và thứ đó đang giết dần thằng bé." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__130__M__1
TT 19859 "Để tôi đoán... Chết chóc, chiến tranh, dịch hạch và đói kém." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__150__M__1
TT 19860 "Tôi thì thấy hoang đường từ đầu chí cuối..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__180__M__1
TT 19861 "Ao tù nước đọng thì hiếm khi có ma thuật lắm nhóc ạ." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__260__M__1
TT 19862 "Hình như nơi này còn rộng hơn nữa... Đằng sau kia." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__430_LIGHT__320__M__1
TT 19863 "Mấy lão giả kim đó đã thuật lại hết những gì xảy ra với Vật Chủ. Ghi chép được xếp theo ngày tháng... Bản chép cuối cùng là vào năm 541..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__020__M__1
TT 19864 "Từ hồi ở tu viện đến giờ tôi chưa ôn lại tiếng Latin, nhưng tóm lại là có nhắc đến Basilius..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__040__M__1
TT 19865 "...và một người tên “Aelia Dragas”. Là... “Hộ Vệ”." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__046__M__1
TT 19866 "Hội Giả Kim đã tách Vật Chủ khỏi cô ta. Cô ta đã làm phản và rồi bị bắt giải đến một “tòa tháp hình trụ tròn”, họ áp giải cô ta tới một... “capella”, là nhà nguyện, trong một pháo đài." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__060__M__1
TT 19867 "Ở đây không ghi." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__066__M__1
TT 19868 "Cũng may là bây giờ họ mới đến." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__110__M__1
TT 19869 "Chui qua kia?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__165__M__1
TT 19870 "Thử đi." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__440_THE_LOCATION__190__M__1
TT 19871 "Thử ra khơi nguyên một tuần với thủy thủ đoàn của tôi xem... khứu giác được tu tiên đắc đạo đến suốt đời." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED__020__M__1
TT 19872 "Nhóc không muốn biết chuyện gì đã xảy ra với Aelia sao? Và cả... “tổ tiên” của nhóc nữa?" VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED__060__M__1
TT 19873 "Khụ..." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__450_CROWNED_ONOM__020__M__1
TT 19874 "Mạo hiểm... nhưng cũng khá thuyết phục." VO__SOPHIA__CH09__RTC__FIRST_RITUALS__110__M__1
TT 19875 "You all right?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__020__M__1
TT 19876 "Damn... bastard..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__027__M__1
TT 19877 "Ha... I... promised myself I'd never... do that again..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__050__M__1
TT 19878 "Yes, well... just try not to get yourself killed..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_EVENT_KNIFE__070__M__1
TT 19879 "What was that?! This is madness! You never said..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__030__M__1
TT 19880 "Just... go talk to him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__050__M__1
TT 19881 "I need... some time." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AFTER_STRIKE__060__M__1
TT 19882 "Amicia?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__010__M__1
TT 19883 "Damn..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__050__M__1
TT 19884 "When you may need me the most? No." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_IS_BACK__070__M__1
TT 19885 "I... I wanted to ask you—are you sure about all this? It seems like a heavy burden for him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__020__M__1
TT 19886 "Listen, we may not know each other well but... You're chasing ghosts. Ghosts that scare him." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__040__M__1
TT 19887 "I can't... The question is, does he need more?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__060__M__1
TT 19888 "I believe you... Fine." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__AMICIA_SOPHIA__080__M__1
TT 19889 "They're pretty heavily armed for slavers." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARMORED_SLAVERS_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 19890 "You know what's waiting for us inside the fort, right?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARMY_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19891 "No..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARRESTED_SLAVERS_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19892 "A lot can happen when there's money to be made..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__ARRESTED_SLAVERS_IDLE__040__M__1
TT 19893 "Yes... who knows what story lies behind it..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__020__M__1
TT 19894 "Some survive... Some are taken by the sea and sleep forever, cradled by the waves." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__040__M__1
TT 19895 "Then they become crab food." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__060__M__1
TT 19896 "Anytime." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BABY_BOAT__090__M__1
TT 19897 "Maybe we'll see some fire jumping and other... safe activities." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_ON_TRACK__030__M__1
TT 19898 "No, but... that symbol could be our chapel?... That “capella” where they took her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__020__M__1
TT 19899 "It's a drawing... So, knowing the sanctuary's there, I think it's on the way to that big decorated tree, probably past the windmills." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_MAP__027__M__1
TT 19900 "Well, I can provide you with whatever you want!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__020__M__1
TT 19901 "We'll... finish here, and I'll take you on a trip, yes?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__050__M__1
TT 19902 "Soon." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__070__M__1
TT 19903 "Deal." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BACK_TO_TOPIC__090__M__1
TT 19904 "What?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__030__M__1
TT 19905 "Amicia, we've got a dead man here!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__080__M__1
TT 19906 "We need to be." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BAD_SIGNS__100__M__1
TT 19907 "Not their hideout, obviously..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BASEMENT__020__M__1
TT 19908 "Give me a moment..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BEFORE_SERIOUS_TALK__010__M__1
TT 19909 "Poor girl didn't have much of a brighter future..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES__060__M__1
TT 19910 "Milo's work..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES_TORCHES__030__M__1
TT 19911 "So there's something there..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BODIES_TORCHES__050__M__1
TT 19912 "Worm eaten..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__010__M__1
TT 19913 "That bridge looks about to collapse..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__030__M__1
TT 19914 "There's a rope and a grapple on this pole!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIDGE_TUTO__050__M__1
TT 19915 "Either they don't know or they don't care." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BRIGHTER_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19916 "Milo said he worked for the Countess. She and the Count probably gave them this place..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BUSINESS_IDLE__010__M__1
TT 19917 "Yes. Dirty business." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__BUSINESS_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 19918 "And there goes our way in..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CART_BRIDGE__040__M__1
TT 19919 "I agree." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CART_BRIDGE_IN__030__M__1
TT 19920 "Loud indeed. We should move." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_DOOR__020__M__1
TT 19921 "Hopefully no one heard that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_DROP__010__M__1
TT 19922 "Be quick, please..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_HOLD__010__M__1
TT 19923 "It lifts a chandelier... A big one!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_MOVING__010__M__1
TT 19924 "The chain still looks pretty solid!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_MOVING__050__M__1
TT 19925 "Go on!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHANDELIER_PULL__020__M__1
TT 19926 "It's barbaric..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_COURTYARD__015__M__1
TT 19927 "Look, on the door... Your Order's symbol..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_COURTYARD__055__M__1
TT 19928 "Listen to me now! Stop this!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_EIGHTH_IDLE__020__M__1
TT 19929 "They're pretty recent. Who did this? Milo?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_ENTER__015__M__1
TT 19930 "So, what?... This chapel was dedicated to her?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_ENTER__030__M__1
TT 19931 "Stay down, Hugo!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FIFTH_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 19932 "Amicia! We have to get inside the chapel! There's no other way!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FINAL_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 19933 "What are you doing?! Hey! Stop!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FINAL_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 19934 "No! Not yet!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_FIRST_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 19935 "You're not doing anything, boy!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_NINTH_WAVE__020__M__1
TT 19936 "Hugo! Let her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__020__M__1
TT 19937 "Amicia! It's getting urgent!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SEVENTH_WAVE__070__M__1
TT 19938 "Calm down! Remember what your sister told you!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_SIXTH_WAVE__030__M__1
TT 19939 "It's going to end badly, Amicia! There has to be a way out!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_THIRD_WAVE__010__M__1
TT 19940 "No! You stay there!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHAPEL_THIRD_WAVE__040__M__1
TT 19941 "This Child thing is a beacon for lunatics..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CHILD_IDLE__030__M__1
TT 19942 "What the hell?!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLIFF_FALL_REACTION__030__M__1
TT 19943 "Well spotted! That's our way in." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSE_ROPE_BOLT__020__M__1
TT 19944 "Time to take a little look around?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE__020__M__1
TT 19945 "So looks like we're conquering it, after all!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__020__M__1
TT 19946 "So you'll rule this thing?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__040__M__1
TT 19947 "A royal contract! I'm honoured!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__060__M__1
TT 19948 "Oh, right. The fort and its chapel..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CLOSED_GATE_VAULT__080__M__1
TT 19949 "Now come down!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__COME_DOWN__010__M__1
TT 19950 "Letting it sink in..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CONTINUE_CHECK__020__M__1
TT 19951 "Rats..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CONTINUE_CHECK__040__M__1
TT 19952 "No use. We should go." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CRANK__020__M__1
TT 19953 "They're everywhere... just like... murderers and traitors." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CROSSING_VILLAGE__020__M__1
TT 19954 "Where the hell is Milo?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__CRYPT_ENTER__010__M__1
TT 19955 "Yes... Good work..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR__010__M__1
TT 19956 "That door looks like it's been stuck for a long time..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_LOCKED__005__M__1
TT 19957 "Yes... We'll need a big push..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_LOCKED__020__M__1
TT 19958 "I think... for now..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__DOOR_OPEN__020__M__1
TT 19959 "It's exhausting... But it's life." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__EXIT__060__M__1
TT 19960 "A cunning bird! It managed to make people believe it's evil..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER__050__M__1
TT 19961 "You should see me when I wake up. I'm the evilest." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER__100__M__1
TT 19962 "It still can be." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FEATHER_PATH__020__M__1
TT 19963 "They're here too..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_CROSS__030__M__1
TT 19964 "Yes... Bloody little opportunists..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_EXTINGUISHED__030__M__1
TT 19965 "Now... either it works... or I'm dead... I can't believe I'm doing this..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRE_LIT__020__M__1
TT 19966 "Damn..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL__010__M__1
TT 19967 "Never seen you do... that." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__FIRST_KILL__030__M__1
TT 19968 "Let's do this together..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__GATE_HALLWAY__030__M__1
TT 19969 "Look at them... They sure know how to celebrate!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__030__M__1
TT 19970 "They don't need it. And WE don't need them to know." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__050__M__1
TT 19971 "You just need to bounce back from this." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__070__M__1
TT 19972 "You... think of something else!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FESTIVAL_TALK__090__M__1
TT 19973 "Well, a piece of it at least..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FLOWERPATH__020__M__1
TT 19974 "And that sanctuary still had a LOT to tell..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FLOWERPATH__050__M__1
TT 19975 "Hey, if you don't know where to go, don't forget about that map." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_FOREST_NOMAP__010__M__1
TT 19976 "So... that was... I don't even know what that was..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_GOINGDOWN_START__005__M__1
TT 19977 "Pragmatic! I like that! Why not check that map again, unless you know where that tower is?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_GOINGDOWN_START__020__M__1
TT 19978 "Here we are! Looks like the real festivities have begun!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_NEW_THINGS__010__M__1
TT 19979 "My mother came from a wealthy family. They weren't exactly pleased when they found out my father was a smuggler. So off to a convent I went— to “cleanse” me of his sins." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__010__M__1
TT 19980 "I'd rather be a sinner and be free. So I escaped. I joined my father, and..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__030__M__1
TT 19981 "Hey, look around you. It's fine. We're centuries later, right?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_SOPHIA_STORY__070__M__1
TT 19982 "Hm. It's quiet... I think they're all at this feast." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__HUB2_VILLAGE_NOMAP__010__M__1
TT 19983 "Their leader..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_CHAPEL__005__M__1
TT 19984 "Milo. I know that name. Roams around the Mediterranean coasts. He's a butcher." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_CHAPEL__020__M__1
TT 19985 "Can't believe you've been through all this before..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_FORT_1__010__M__1
TT 19986 "I'm sorry for you, Hugo... But there'll be better times." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__IDLE_FORT_5__010__M__1
TT 19987 "How can you be so calm?..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_CART__020__M__1
TT 19988 "Obviously. Stupid question..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_CART__040__M__1
TT 19989 "Are you hurt?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTERACT_FALL__040__M__1
TT 19990 "I'd say... slavers, by the looks of it..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__110__M__1
TT 19991 "They capture people... And sell them like animals..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__INTRO_SLAVES__130__M__1
TT 19992 "Shhh... Easy." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILL_FORT_2__020__M__1
TT 19993 "We need to reach that chapel fast..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILL_FORT_3__020__M__1
TT 19994 "That was a bit excessive, no?" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILLED_ALL_FORT__020__M__1
TT 19995 "Let's just... move forward, please." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KILLED_ALL_FORT__040__M__1
TT 19996 "Shit!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__060__M__1
TT 19997 "No... No!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__075__M__1
TT 19998 "Get... your hands... off her!" VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__KNIFE_EVENT__080__M__1
TT 19999 "Try not to think about that..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__CHATTER__LADY_IDLE__020__M__1
