TT 20113 "And, for some stupid reason, I like you. And I like you at the shittiest worst of your life, right? I'm fine with that. Even the strangest things happen for a reason. Sailors stories are full of it. That said..." VO__SOPHIA__CH10__RTC__510_END__155__M__1
